build

public PendingRequest build(Uri origin)
Build PendingRequest using origin.

Following rules apply:

  • Builder contains component package and class name -> returned request contains them
  • Builder contains component class name only -> returned request has package name from origin and class name from builder
  • Builder contains no component name -> returned request has component package and class name from origin
  • Builder contains dispatch package name -> returned request has dispatch package name and id (defaults to 0) from builder
  • Builder contains no dispatch package name and non-zero dispatch id -> returned request has dispatch package name from origin and dispatch id from builder
  • Builder contains no dispatch package name and zero dispatch id -> returned request has null dispatch

Parameters:
origin - Uri to extract missing data from
Returns:
Newly created PendingRequest
